graph TD
    START([Start]) --> INIT[Initialize State + Empty Plan]
    INIT --> MCP[Connect to Brave Search MCP Server]
    MCP --> CHECK{More questions<br/>AND under iteration limit<br/>AND not complete?}

    CHECK -->|Yes| POP[Pop next question]
    POP --> AGENT[Run Research Agent<br/>with state + plan context]
    AGENT --> UPDATE[Update findings,<br/>sources, questions]
    UPDATE --> PLAN[Update Research Plan]
    PLAN --> GOAL{Agent says<br/>goal satisfied?}
    GOAL -->|Yes| DONE[Mark complete]
    GOAL -->|No| CHECK
    DONE --> CHECK

    CHECK -->|No| SYNTH[Run Synthesis Agent<br/>with findings + plan]
    SYNTH --> REPORT([Output Research Report])

    style CHECK fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#FF9800
    style AGENT fill:#e8f4f8,stroke:#2196F3
    style PLAN fill:#e8f8e8,stroke:#4CAF50
    style SYNTH fill:#f3e8f4,stroke:#9C27B0
